name: Simple_Living_5-piece_Burntwood_Dining_Set_
reviews: Some assembly was required, but it was simple to do. Set is sturdy and beautiful.

Can't be happier with this dining set! Put together by myself in a few hours and the table and chairs are very sturdy. Although it has a veneer, you would never know looking at it or feeling it. Only regret is not getting the set with six chairs!
Sturdy and easy to put together. Looks great in our kitchen!

When i opened the box and seen and felt this wood, i was in LOVE. Its so beautiful and the quality is excellent! I am also a single mom with a 16 month old running around. i was able to put it together ALONE! so easy!!!

The order arrived sooner than expected. It was very easy to put together. It is a strong, sturdy set. It looks like barnwood or reclaimed wood. The set it's easy to keep clean, even the seat cushions. For the price size and free shipping one can not go wrong with this item. We are very pleased!
Super high quality - table is small but looks expensive. Easy to assemble.
i just got this table few weeks ago and its such poor quality the chair broke already :(
